## 🖥️ UI Pages (`app/`)

*   **`/`**: Landing home page ([app/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/AIO12TH-RTX30WHITE/bakaboria/app/page.tsx)).
*   **`/signIn`**: Authenticates users ([app/signIn/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/AIO12TH-RTX30WHITE/bakaboria/app/signIn/page.tsx)). Integrates Google OAuth via [GoogleSignInBtn.tsx](file:///c:/Users/AIO12TH-RTX30WHITE/bakaboria/app/components/GoogleSignInBtn.tsx) and supports credentials register/login.
*   **`/upload_doc`**: Admin page to register new documents ([app/upload_doc/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/AIO12TH-RTX30WHITE/bakaboria/app/upload_doc/page.tsx)). Allows typing document metadata, tags, toggling advanced visibility details, and pasting a Google Drive link. *(Note: local PDF upload is UI-redirected to Google Drive upload in the template code)*.
*   **`/get_doc`**: Dashboard to search, list, and download documents ([app/get_doc/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/AIO12TH-RTX30WHITE/bakaboria/app/get_doc/page.tsx)). Prompts the user for a password if the target document is protected.
*   **`/terminal`**: A terminal emulator using the Ubuntu Mono font ([app/terminal/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/AIO12TH-RTX30WHITE/bakaboria/app/terminal/page.tsx)) allowing interactive hierarchy queries and parent/child creations matching design aesthetics.
*   **`/gemini_test`**: Diagnostic page ([app/gemini_test/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/AIO12TH-RTX30WHITE/bakaboria/app/gemini_test/page.tsx)) allowing developers to manually input a document ID and witness Gemini's structured analysis JSON response.
